nodes.text: The Mighty Chewbacca in the Forest of Fear! (audiobook)

The Mighty Chewbacca in the Forest of Fear! is the unabridged audio version of the canon novel of the same name, written by Tom Angleberger. It was narrated by January LaVoy, Jonathan Davis, Marc Thompson, Saskia Maarleveld, and Sean Kenin, and released by Listening Library on May 25, 2018.
